---
import { siteConfig } from "../config/site";
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

    <!-- H1 -->
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Memphis Car Accident Attorney â€“ Help With Personal Injury Accident Claims
    </h1>

    <img
  src="/images/memphis-car-accident-attorney-consultation.webp"
  alt="Consulting with car accident attorney in Memphis after accident"
  class="w-full rounded-lg my-6"
/>

    <!-- Paragraph 1 -->
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      If you were involved in a car accident in Memphis, Tennessee, finding reliable legal guidance can be an important step toward protecting your rights and pursuing compensation. We connect accident victims with independent attorneys who handle car accident and personal injury claims in the Memphis area.
    </p>

    <!-- Paragraph 2 -->
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Car accidents often leave people dealing with medical treatment, insurance delays, lost income, and uncertainty about the claims process. You may request a free case evaluation to discuss your accident claim with an attorney who can explain how Tennessee personal injury law may apply to your situation.
    </p>

    <!-- Paragraph 3 + Bullet List -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3">
        Being injured in an accident caused by another driver's negligence creates immediate challenges:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Medical expenses accumulate quickly</li>
        <li>Lost wages affect your family's financial stability</li>
        <li>Pain and suffering disrupts your entire life</li>
        <li>Insurance companies work to minimize your compensation</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Primary CTA -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
  <a
    href={`tel:${siteConfig.phoneRaw}`}
    class="btn-primary"
  >
    Call Today: {siteConfig.phoneDisplay}
  </a>
</div>

</section>
